 id=\"patron\" style=\"color:#549a43;font-size:40px\"><strong>Enrichment Programs<br></strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">In addition to our core curriculum, we provide various enrichment programs that allow children to explore their interests and develop new skills. These programs may include language classes, music lessons, dance, sports, and more.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}}},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2em\",\"right\":\"2em\",\"bottom\":\"2em\",\"left\":\"2em\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"0px\",\"style\":\"none\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"className\":\"rounded-corner-cards\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column rounded-corner-cards has-base-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\"><!-- wp:kadence/image {\"id\":151,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"uniqueID\":\"_0eaf6b-5f\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-kadence-image kb-image_0eaf6b-5f size-full\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/icon-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kb-img wp-image-151\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#549a43\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" id=\"patron\" style=\"color:#549a43;font-size:40px\"><strong>After School Care</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">We offer a safe and stimulating after-school program for school-aged children. Our after-school care includes homework assistance, enrichment activities, and supervised free play, ensuring a balanced experience for children after their regular school hours.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"align\":\"full\",\"mediaId\":10,\"mediaLink\":\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/my-family-is/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"large\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#d99036\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignfull is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center has-background\" style=\"background-color:#d99036\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dreamstime_18807433-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10 size-large\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"textColor\":\"base\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-base-color has-text-color\"><strong>Our Staff</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#d99036\"}},\"textColor\":\"base\",\"fontSize\":\"extra-small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-base-color has-text-color has-background has-extra-small-font-size\" style=\"background-color:#d99036\">Apple Tree House Learning Academy boasts a team of highly qualified and experienced educators who are passionate about working with children. Our teachers undergo continuous professional development to stay updated with the latest educational practices and create a nurturing learning environment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>