und creating a safe, inclusive, and engaging environment that promotes exploration, creativity, and critical thinking. We strive to inspire a lifelong love for learning, empower children to discover their potential, and nurture their social, emotional, cognitive, and physical development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/column -->\n<!-- /wp:kadence/rowlayout -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"0\"},\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\"}}},\"backgroundColor\":\"tertiary\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide has-tertiary-background-color has-background\" style=\"margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}}},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2em\",\"right\":\"2em\",\"bottom\":\"2em\",\"left\":\"2em\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"0px\",\"style\":\"none\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"className\":\"rounded-corner-cards\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column rounded-corner-cards has-base-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\"><!-- wp:kadence/image {\"id\":154,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"uniqueID\":\"_3c5f49-3c\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-kadence-image kb-image_3c5f49-3c size-full\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/icon-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kb-img wp-image-154\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#549a43\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" id=\"single\" style=\"color:#549a43;font-size:40px\"><strong>Early Childhood Education</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#000000\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-css-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#000000;color:#000000\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We offer a high-quality early childhood education program for children aged 2 to 5 years. Our curriculum focuses on play-based learning, literacy, numeracy, science, art, music, and social skills development. We aim to create a solid foundation for future academic success.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}}},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2em\",\"right\":\"2em\",\"bottom\":\"2em\",\"left\":\"2em\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"0px\",\"style\":\"none\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"className\":\"rounded-corner-cards\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column rounded-corner-cards has-base-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\"><!-- wp:kadence/image {\"id\":152,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"uniqueID\":\"_421c87-31\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-kadence-image kb-image_421c87-31 size-full\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/icon-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kb-img wp-image-152\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#549a43\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" id=\"family\" style=\"color:#549a43;font-size:40px\"><strong>Parental Involvement<br></strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"}},\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.5\">We believe in establishing a strong partnership with parents and encourage their active involvement in their child\'s learning journey. We organize regular parent-teacher meetings, workshops, and events to foster communication, collaboration, and shared decision-making.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}}},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2em\",\"right\":\"2em\",\"bottom\":\"2em\",\"left\":\"2em\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"0px\",\"style\":\"none\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"className\":\"rounded-corner-cards\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column rounded-corner-cards has-base-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\"><!-- wp:kadence/image {\"id\":153,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"uniqueID\":\"_1dcdff-03\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-kadence-image kb-image_1dcdff-03 size-full\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/icon-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kb-img wp-image-153\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#549a43\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" id=\"patron\" style=\"color:#549a43;font-size:40px\"><strong>Enrichment Programs<br></strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:se