"],\"right\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"bottom\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"left\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"unit\":\"px\"}],\"tabletMarkBorderStyles\":[{\"top\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"right\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"bottom\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"left\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"unit\":\"px\"}],\"mobileMarkBorderStyles\":[{\"top\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"right\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"bottom\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"left\":[null,\"\",\"\"],\"unit\":\"px\"}],\"anchor\":\"about-us\"} -->\n<h2 id=\"about-us\" class=\"kt-adv-heading_5be474-11 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading\" data-kb-block=\"kb-adv-heading_5be474-11\">About Us</h2>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/advancedheading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apple Tree House Learning Academy is an innovative and nurturing educational institution committed to the growth and development of young minds. Our academy offers a comprehensive range of programs and services designed to support children\'s learning and foster their overall well-being.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Apple Tree House Learning Academy, we believe that each child is unique and possesses an innate curiosity and eagerness to learn. Our philosophy is centered around creating a safe, inclusive, and engaging environment that promotes exploration, creativity, and critical thinking. We strive to inspire a lifelong love for learning, empower children to discover their potential, and nurture their social, emotional, cognitive, and physical development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/column -->\n<!-- /wp:kadence/rowlayout -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"0\"},\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\"}}},\"backgroundColor\":\"tertiary\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide has-tertiary-background-color has-background\" style=\"margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);paddin