re</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">We offer a safe and stimulating after-school program for school-aged children. Our after-school care includes homework assistance, enrichment activities, and supervised free play, ensuring a balanced experience for children after their regular school hours.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"align\":\"full\",\"mediaId\":193,\"mediaLink\":\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/hometest/girl-looking-at-figures/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"large\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#d99036\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|80\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|80\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|80\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|80\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignfull is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center has-background\" style=\"background-color:#d99036;margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80);margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80)\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/girl-looking-at-figures.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-193 size-large\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"textColor\":\"base\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-base-color has-text-color\"><strong><strong>Our Staff</strong></strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"base\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-base-color has-text-color\">Apple 