-equipped classrooms, age-appropriate learning materials, indoor and outdoor play areas, a library, and other amenities to support children\'s holistic development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"base\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-base-color has-text-color\">We invite you to visit <strong><em>Apple Tree House Learning Academy</em></strong>, where we prioritize the growth, happiness, and success of every child in our care. Feel free to contact us for more information or to schedule a tour of our facility.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/children-jumping.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-189 size-large\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->','test','','inherit','closed','closed','','8-revision-v1','','','2023-06-18 18:54:06','2023-06-18 18:54:06','',8,'http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/?p=300',0,'revision','',0),(301,4,'2023-06-18 18:55:13','2023-06-18 18:55:13','<!-- wp:kadence/rowlayout {\"uniqueID\":\"_660305-ae\",\"colLayout\":\"row\",\"minHeight\":100,\"maxWidth\":100,\"bgImg\":\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/children-bg-img.jpg\",\"overlay\":\"#000000\",\"overlayFirstOpacity\":1,\"overlayOpacity\":75,\"align\":\"center\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"middle\",\"minHeightUnit\":\"vh\",\"maxWidthUnit\":\"vw\",\"kbVersion\":2} -->\n<!-- wp:kadence/column {\"borderWidth\":[\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"uniqueID\":\"_1c8bbf-61\",\"borderStyle\":[{\"top\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"right\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"bottom\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"left\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"unit\":\"px\"}]} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column_1c8bbf-61\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\"><!-- wp:kadence/column {\"borderWidth\":[\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"uniqueID\":\"_925f74-19\",\"textAlign\":[\"center\",\"\",\"\"],\"borderStyle\":[{\"top\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"right\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"bottom\":[\"\",\