e Tree House Learning Academy</em></strong> is an innovative and nurturing educational institution committed to the growth and development of young minds. Our academy offers a comprehensive range of programs and services designed to support children\'s learning and foster their overall well-being.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At <strong><em>Apple Tree House Learning Academy</em></strong>, we believe that each child is unique and possesses an innate curiosity and eagerness to learn. Our philosophy is centered around creating a safe, inclusive, and engaging environment that promotes exploration, creativity, and critical thinking. We strive to inspire a lifelong love for learning, empower children to discover their potential, and nurture their social, emotional, cognitive, and physical development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/column -->\n<!-- /wp:kadence/rowlayout -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"0\"},\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|80\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|80\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\"}}},\"backgroundColor\":\"tertiary\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide has-tertiary-background-color has-background\" id=\"services\" style=\"margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\"><!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}}},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2em\",\"right\":\"2em\",\"bottom\":\"2em\",\"left\":\"2em\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"0px\",\"style\":\"none\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"className\":\"rounded-corner-cards\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column rounded-corner-cards has-base-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\"><!-- wp:kadence/image {\"id\":154,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"uniqueID\":\"_94aa1a-9a\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-kadence-image kb-image_94aa1a-9a size-full\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/icon-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kb-img wp-image-154\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#549a43\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" id=\"single\" style=\"color:#549a43;font-size:40px\"><strong>Early Childhood Education</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#000000\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-css-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#000000;color:#000000\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We offer a high-quality early childhood education program for children aged 2 to 5 years. Our curriculum focuses on play-based learning, literacy, numeracy, science, art, music, and social skills development. We aim to create a solid foundation for future academic success.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}}},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2em\",\"right\":\"2em\",\"bottom\":\"2em\",\"left\":\"2em\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"0px\",\"style\":\"none\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"className\":\"rounded-corner-cards\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column rounded-corner-cards has-base-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\"><!-- wp:kadence/image {\"id\":152,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"uniqueID\":\"_1605ab-a5\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-kadence-image kb-image_1605ab-a5 size-full\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/icon-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kb-img wp-image-152\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#549a43\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" id=\"family\" style=\"color:#549a43;font-size:40px\"><strong>Parental Involvement<br></strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"}},\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.5\">We believe in establishing a strong partnership with parents and encourage their active involvement in their child\'s learning journey. We organize regular parent-teacher meetings, workshops, and events to foster communication, collaboration, and shared decision-making.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}}},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2em\",\"right\":\"2em\",\"bottom\":\"2em\",\"left\":\"2em\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"0px\",\"style\":\"none\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"className\":\"rounded-corner-cards\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column rounded-corner-cards has-base-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\"><!-- wp:kadence/image {\"id\":153,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"uniqueID\":\"_b2da3b-46\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-kadence-image kb-image_b2da3b-46 size-full\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/icon-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kb-img wp-image-153\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#549a43\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" id=\"patron\" style=\"color:#549a43;font-size:40px\"><strong>Enrichment Programs<br></strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">In addition to our core curriculum, we provide various enrichment programs that allow children to explore their interests and develop new skills. These programs may include language classes, music lessons, dance, sports, and more.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}}},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2em\",\"right\":\"2em\",\"bottom\":\"2em\",\"left\":\"2em\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"0px\",\"style\":\"none\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"className\":\"rounded-corner-cards\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column rounded-corner-cards has-base-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\"><!-- wp:kadence/image {\"id\":151,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"uniqueID\":\"_969a61-36\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-kadence-image kb-image_969a61-36 size-full\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/icon-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kb-img wp-image-151\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#549a43\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" id=\"patron\" style=\"color:#549a43;font-size:40px\"><strong>After School Care</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">We offer a safe and stimulating after-school program for school-aged children. Our after-school care includes homework assistance, enrichment activities, and supervised free play, ensuring a balanced experience for children after their regular school hours.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"align\":\"full\",\"mediaId\":193,\"mediaLink\":\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/hometest/girl-looking-at-figures/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"large\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#d99036\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignfull is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center has-background\" style=\"background-color:#d99036;margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60)\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/girl-looking-at-figures.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-193 size-large\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"textColor\":\"base\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-base-color has-text-color\"><strong><strong>Our Staff</strong></strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"base\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-base-color has-text-color\"><strong><em>Apple Tree House Learning Academy</em></strong> boasts a team of highly qualified and experienced educators who are passionate about working with children. Our teachers undergo continuous professional development to stay updated with the latest educational practices and create a nurturing learning environment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"align\":\"full\",\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":189,\"mediaLink\":\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/hometest/children-jumping/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"large\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#97bf41\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignfull has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center has-background\" style=\"background-color:#97bf41;margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60)\"><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"textColor\":\"base\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-base-color has-text-color\"><strong>Our Facilit</strong>y</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"base\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-base-color has-text-color\">Our academy features well-equipped classrooms, age-appropriate learning materials, indoor and outdoor play areas, a library, and other amenities to support children\'s holistic development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"base\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-base-color has-text-color\">We invite you to visit <strong><em>Apple Tree House Learning Academy</em></strong>, where we prioritize the growth, happiness, and success of every child in our care. Feel free to contact us for more information or to schedule a tour of our facility.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/children-jumping.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-189 size-large\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->','test','','inherit','closed','closed','','8-revision-v1','','','2023-06-18 19:01:31','2023-06-18 19:01:31','',8,'http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/?p=303',0,'revision','',0),(304,4,'2023-06-18 19:02:05','2023-06-18 19:02:05','','Posts','','publish','closed','closed','','posts','','','2023-06-18 21:46:08','2023-06-18 21:46:08','',0,'http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/?page_id=304',0,'page','',0),(305,4,'2023-06-18 19:02:05','2023-06-18 19:02:05','','Posts','','inherit','closed','closed','','304-revision-v1','','','2023-06-18 19:02:05','2023-06-18 19:02:05','',304,'http://appletreehouselearningacademy.com/?p=305',0,'revision','',0);
